<div class="ru-story">
<div class="w75 right"><img width="75" height="75" border="0" alt="Making It Harder to Prove White-Collar Crimes" src="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2015/12/01/business/db-whitecollar-web1/db-whitecollar-web1-square320.jpg"/></div>
